<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạlʿạlm ybny wyzrʿ .. wtmly msẖ sẖbʿạn)2
 (hmh ylbs wyqlʿ .. wʿn yswʿ gẖflạn)2
 ạlqrạr- (lkn ạ̉nạ msẖ mn hnạ .. dh hnạ ʿạlm fạny)2
 (lạ mạl wlạ jạh wlạ gẖny̱ .. ạ̉nạ lyã wṭn tạny)2
